! 2.5.0

* Added recurrence quick actions, RRULE summaries, and occurrence-aware recurrence editing in create and preview popups.
* Restored the reliable post-display caption focus fallback for the create-event modal and documented why the native focus attribute alone is not enough there.
* Updated lint and typecheck compatibility for the current TypeScript toolchain.

! 2.4.2

* Added a native date picker entry point on the calendar title for quick date jumping.
* Added agenda timeline styling for list views.
* Fixed search result ordering so newer items appear above older items on the same page.

